HEADWORD: Agrestic
<hw>A*gres"tic</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>agrestis</ets>, fr. <ets>ager</ets> field.]</ety> <def>Pertaining
